The paper deals with data augmentation for visual recognition systems, specifically object detection and semantic segmentation. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also proposes a context model using a convolutional neural network, which falls under the machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) tasks such as scene understanding, which falls under the computational linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category. Finally, the paper deals with image manipulation techniques, which falls under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
